        <h2 style="font-size: var(--fluid-h3);">Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Artificial Intelligence is transforming how we work, learn, and live. But too often, conversations about AI are filled with jargon, hype, or fear-mongering. We believe Newark residents deserve better.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our mission is to provide <strong>honest, accessible AI education</strong> that helps people understand what AI really is, how it can help them, and what they need to know to use it safely and effectively.
        </p>
        
